165
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:11,070
Je to povedomé, však?

166
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:17,180
Diamantový sneh ...

167
00:16:17,580 --> 00:16:19,580
Videli sme ho spolu.

168
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:21,680
Takže to fungovalo?

169
